data.description: Looking for a move-in ready home that's conveniently located in Gulf Shores? Look no further! This home features a new roof, (2021) open floor plan with vaulted ceilings, stainless appliances, granite counter tops, and tile throughout. The kitchen also includes a sit-down bar and sunny breakfast room make cooking a breeze. The separate dining room has a custom Murphy bed with easy pull-down to accommodate extra sleeping quarters. The split bedroom plan has a primary bathroom with custom sinks, garden tub, separate shower, and block glass accents. Big closets in all bedrooms provide ample storage space. The spacious living room and family room include a cozy wood-burning fireplace. The fenced backyard has privacy and views to the Craft Farms Golf Course, and you can enjoy a spacious patio for grilling and outdoor entertaining. Located in Gulf Shores City School District. Assumable FHA Mortgage with 3.5% interest rate.
